original_title: One Hour Beginners Bedtime Yoga | with Chelsey Jones
overview: Join Chelsey Jones in this 1 hour beginners Bedtime Yoga class, that will bring the heat & wind down the pace to put you into a relaxing mood to get a gentle nights sleep. This class is great for beginners!
tagline: A 1 yoga flow for bedtime, an excellent way to end the day and release any negative energy.
title: One Hour Beginners Bedtime Yoga | with Chelsey Jones
